Show HN: Simple golinks server backed by airtable
text:
Like short codes? Like bookmarks? Have fun with this very simple golinks server.

If you haven't heard of golinks, they are short codes to bookmarks. In your browser you type `go/<code>` and it takes you to a bookmark. Eg, `go/hn` or `go hn` (space is easier to type than forward slash) could take you to https://news.ycombinator.com. Happy Holidays!
